## Acknowledgements

This harness is a simplified take on the **sandcastle** agent harness pattern.
Several Dockerfile patterns (the `node` → `agent` user rename at UID 1000,
`PIP_BREAK_SYSTEM_PACKAGES=1`, and the official Claude CLI install path)
are adopted from `.sandcastle/Dockerfile`. If sandcastle is distributed
under MIT, its original copyright notice and license terms continue to
apply to those portions; add the upstream LICENSE under `LICENSES/` when
redistributing.
